GUILTY plea entered to the charge.  Convicted.
Sentence Withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for twelve (12) months.
Conditions of probation:
1) AODA assessment and follow through;
2) Pay court costs;
3) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
4) provide DNA sample.
The Court will entertain a motion for early discharge from probation if assessment and follow through is completed and it is recommended by the agent.
